WEBVTT

00:00.417 --> 00:02.085
<i>Previously on Mad Men...</i>

00:02.169 --> 00:04.505
I've seen that look,
and he is in love with you too.

00:04.671 --> 00:06.089
Nothing can happen.

00:06.173 --> 00:07.799
We are going to
get Ocean Spray.

00:07.966 --> 00:10.677
So you need to stop
chasing Sunkist.

00:12.137 --> 00:13.305
Oh, God...

00:14.014 --> 00:15.307
You make me sick!

00:15.474 --> 00:16.725
Sally!

00:16.850 --> 00:18.977
We want you to familiarize
yourself with Chevy.

00:19.311 --> 00:21.355
That is music to my ears.

00:21.688 --> 00:24.441
When there's true love,
it doesn't matter who it is.

00:25.776 --> 00:27.528
I don't know where you've gone,

00:27.694 --> 00:29.780
something has to change.

00:31.000 --> 00:37.074
